e=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Software Features (Intro)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_layout=\"light\"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">The right solution for your organisation</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We have five different license levels, taking you from an entry level solution to our Pro editions that deliver unparalleled features.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Connect your card to unlimited databases, web services and sophisticated contactless encoding applications. We have it all. Need biometric record lookup? We have it. Need to control what every user can see and do? We can do it. Want to run on a network spread over the world? We can do it.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our customers include critical infrastructure facilities, banks, universities, airports, hospitals, and more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/et_pb_text][et_pb_code admin_label=\"Editions Overview (Don\'t Edit)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\"][editions][/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]</p>', 'Home Page', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'design-and-print-professional-id-cards', '', '', '2018-01-24 16:25:07', '2018-01-24 16:25:07', '', 0, 'https://wordpress.mac/?page_id=39', 0, 'page', '', 0),
