(204, 1, '2018-01-24 16:24:46', '2018-01-24 16:24:46', '[et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_class=\"section lightBlue\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_class=\"paper\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"How it works\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Secure ID issuance in three easy steps</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\">TrustID’s straightforward configuration is scalable for any ID scheme and takes you from card design right through to issuance.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">[showmodule id=\"128\"]\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_class=\"lightGrey\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Software Features (Intro)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Featured packed ID design software</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. ``</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" make_equal=\"on\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Smart card encoding capability\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"https://testing.trustidsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Ultrasecure-access-control.jpg\" alt=\"Smart card encoding capability\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">  Inline card encoding</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">All TrustID editions support the writing of electronic data to magnetic stripe cards.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">  For inline smart card printing and encoding use the Pro-Smart edition for MIFARE® Classic® and Pro-Smart+ for MIFARE® DESFire EV1 or MIFARE® SAM AV2 technologies.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Create dynamic QR codes and barcodes\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"https://testing.trustidsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-barcodes-1.jpg\" alt=\"Create dynamic QR codes and barcodes\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Create a unique experience for each user</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">With the powerful user profile feature, you can customise permissions of what each user can see and do when they login to TrustID.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Data integration at the touch of a button\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"https://testing.trustidsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-Integration.jpg\" alt=\"Data integration at the touch of a button\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Scalable database integration</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The TrustID suite offers a comprehensive range of database connectivity choices. These start with simple CSV and text and include MS Access and MS Excel.  Enterprise level databases such as MYSQL, Oracle and ODBC can be integrated with all Pro editions.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Advanced camera and asset support\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"https://testing.trustidsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-camera-support2.jpg\" alt=\"Advanced camera and asset support\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Support for all your ID peripherals</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">TrustID supports a wide range of devices. Photographs can be added using webcams, scanners and Canon digital cameras. Signature capture is available on most editions, and automatic face recognition is available on Pro licenses. Pro Smart editions include biometric capture, storage and verification.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"See a live preview of every card\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"https://testing.trustidsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/trustid-user.jpg\" alt=\"See a live preview of every card\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Manage from one location</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Enterprise editions offer centralised data and license management. You can store all your card layouts, database connections, printer settings, and more in one location. Having shared data enables all users to have the most current information.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"TrustID works with any printer, any card\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"https://testing.trustidsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-any-printer.jpg\" alt=\"TrustID works with any printer, any card\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">TrustID works with any printer, any card</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Although it is optimised for the Magicard range of secure ID card printers, TrustID will work with most other ID issuance hardware. Text is crisp and images are vibrant. The software can also be used to encode both magnetic stripe and contactless or contact chip smart cards.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_class=\"white showIcon wizard\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" background_size=\"initial\" make_fullwidth=\"on\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Meet the ID design wizard\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Meet the ID design wizard</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. ```.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_code admin_label=\"Wizaerd Carasel {Don\'t Edit}\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\"][carasel][/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_class=\"lightBlue\" global_module=\"133\"][et_pb_row global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" background_size=\"initial\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"4 Clicks Text\" global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Design to print in 4 clicks</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The four click user interface makes day-to-day operation simple. In just a few clicks you can find a record, enter/edit/delete data, take a photo and print a card.</p>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" make_equal=\"on\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" background_size=\"initial\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Search/Select Records\" global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[showIcon icon=\"icons-mag\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Search/Select Records</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Edit Record\" global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[showIcon icon=\"icons-pencil\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Edit Record</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Add a Photo \" global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[showIcon icon=\"icons-camera\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Add a Photo</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Print Your Card\" global_parent=\"133\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[showIcon icon=\"icons-rio\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Print Your Card</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_id=\"featured_video\" module_class=\"blue\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.92\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Featured Video Text\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<p>Getting started is easy. With our FREE trial edition, you can design your card, print samples, setup database options, and more. If you like what you see, simply purchase a license and activate your software.</p><p>Just fill out the form and you will receive an email that includes your download link. Have questions or would like a personal tour of our software? Let us know and we\'ll be happy to help.</p><p>Test-drive your free trial of <strong>TrustID</strong> today .</p><p><a class=\"whiteBtn\" href=\"#\">Download a demo</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_code admin_label=\"TrustID Video (Don\'t Edit)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\"][pageVideo][/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" module_class=\"lightBlue\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Software Features (Intro)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" background_layout=\"light\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">The right solution for your organisation</h2><p>We have five different license levels, taking you from an entry level solution to our Pro editions that deliver unparalleled features.</p><p>Connect your card to unlimited databases, web services and sophisticated contactless encoding applications. We have it all. Need biometric record lookup? We have it. Need to control what every user can see and do? We can do it. Want to run on a network spread over the world? We can do it.</p><p>Our customers include critical infrastructure facilities, banks, universities, airports, hospitals, and more.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_code admin_label=\"Editions Overview (Don\'t Edit)\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\"][editions][/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Home Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 16:24:46', '2018-01-24 16:24:46', '', 39, 'https://testing.trustidsoft.com/?p=204', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
