size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Smart card encoding capability</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">TrustID Pro Smart supports in-line printing and encoding of smart cards for physical and logical access control systems based on MIFARE® Classic® (EV1) and iClass® technologies.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Create dynamic QR codes and barcodes\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"http://wordpress.mac/content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-barcodes-1.jpg\" alt=\"Create dynamic QR codes and barcodes\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Create dynamic QR codes and barcodes</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Full barcode support comes as standard with every edition. TrustID dynamically generates more than 60 types of barcodes including QR codes, Code 39 and UPC.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Data integration at the touch of a button\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"http://wordpress.mac/content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-Integration.jpg\" alt=\"Data integration at the touch of a button\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Data integration at the touch of a button</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Data Integration from Excel, SQL, dBASE, and Microsoft® Access database is seamless using the visual database wizard. Just connect to your database once to bring all your data files and photos into TrustID.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Advanced camera and asset support\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"http://wordpress.mac/content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-camera-support2.jpg\" alt=\"Advanced camera and asset support\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Advanced camera and asset support</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Capture and edit photos, fingerprints and signatures without leaving the program. Use your webcam or digital camera directly from TrustID to help you get the perfect shot every time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"See a live preview of every card\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"http://wordpress.mac/content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-Live-preview-rio-Pro.jpg\" alt=\"See a live preview of every card\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" module_class=\"paper\"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">See a live preview of every card</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">TrustID gives a real time preview of every card during data entry so what you see is what you get. TrustID also monitors your connected printers in real time, so you know how many cards have printed, prints remaining, and when a printer needs to be cleaned.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"TrustID works with any printer, any card\" _builder_version=\"3.0.92\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" image=\"http://wordpress.mac/content/uploads/2018/01/500x350px-any-printer.jpg\" alt=\"TrustID works with any printer, any card\" use_circle=\"off\" use_circle_border=\"off\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=